    DateParser
    DateParser.setDate​(String date)
    Setter method for the date property This method try to parse the string passed in 3 different ways: With the Twitter String date format: yyyy-MM-dd'T'HH:mm:ss.SSS'Z' es: '2022-01-01T14:07:02.000Z'. With a simple String date format: yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss es: 2022-01-01 14:07:02. With the Twitter String date format: HH:mm:ss es: 14:07:02. If all the formats rise a parsing exception catched, than another persing exception will be raised without a catch.
